IDP Education India, a student placement service provider, will organise an Australian education fair in the city at The Gateway Hotel on February 8 for students aspiring to pursue higher education in Australia. The fair will bring together prominent universities and educational institutes from Australia under one roof. Mr. Piyush Kumar, Country Director, India - IDP Education said that 37 Australian institutions would participate in the programme. It is a free platform for all students to gauge their prospects, apply directly to the institution of their choice and get first hand information on courses, scholarships etc.‚Äù